  "slug": "smoked-haddock-and-leek-pie",
  "title": "Smoked Haddock and Leek Pie",
  "subtitle": "Flaked smoked haddock in a cream sauce with leeks, under a puff pastry lid",
  "excerpt": "Smoked haddock has a particular affinity with cream and leeks. This pie uses a simple veloute sauce built from the haddock poaching milk, enriched with cream, and poured over the flaked fish and softened leeks before a puff pastry lid goes on.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Traditional British fish pie tradition. Jane Grigson, Fish Cookery (1973): smoked haddock in cream sauce. Delia Smith, Complete Cookery Course (1978): fish pie method with puff pastry lid.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Smoked haddock is sold in two forms: ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "naturally smoked haddock",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr3sxx0000e0v4tcoit955"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " (pale cream-coloured) and artificially dyed yellow haddock. Either works for this pie, but the natural version has a more delicate, complex smoke. Poach it in milk: the milk becomes the base of a cream ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "veloute",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp5q54if0000lgv4hp1nhdad"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " that carries the smoked flavour through the whole dish.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What you need",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "attrs": {
          "items": [
            {
              "name": "Smoked haddock",
              "unit": "g",
              "amount": 600,
              "prepNote": "skin on, undyed if possible",
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp49f4v1003erkv40cb2vngk",
              "ingredientSlug": "smoked-haddock"
            },
            {
              "name": "Whole milk",
              "unit": "ml",
              "amount": 400,
              "prepNote": "for poaching",
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp49f3be000nrkv4co43fp6z",
              "ingredientSlug": "whole-milk"
            },
            {
              "name": "Leek",
              "unit": "each",
              "amount": 3,
              "prepNote": "cleaned and sliced into rounds",
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp49f5d50048rkv4wuegzd69",
              "ingredientSlug": "leek"
            },
            {
